@startuml Recruiter_Notifications

title Recruiter - Notifications (Module D)

actor Recruiter as "👔 Nhà Tuyển Dụng"

rectangle "NOTIFICATIONS" {
    usecase "View My\nNotifications" as D15
    usecase "Mark Notif\nAs Read" as D16
    usecase "Get Unread\nNotif Count" as D17
    usecase "Mark All\nAs Read" as D18
}

Recruiter --> D15: 1. View notifications
D15 --> D16: 2. Mark as read
Recruiter --> D17: 3. Check unread count
Recruiter --> D18: 4. Mark all as read

note right of D15
  **Priority:** P1 (Important)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
